        {
          "id": "cp_in_t1",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "text-editor",
          "settings": {
            "editor": "<p>For anglers and travelers looking to experience the incredible diversity of Patagonia, we offer a series of combination programs connecting our different operations. Each venue offers a distinct landscape, style of fishing, and atmosphere, allowing guests to experience multiple sides of Patagonia in one seamless journey.</p>",
            "text_color": "#6B7A8D",
            "typography_typography": "custom",
            "typography_font_family": "Bricolage Grotesque",
            "typography_font_size": { "unit": "rem", "size": 1, "sizes": [] },
            "typography_line_height": { "unit": "em", "size": 1.8, "sizes": [] },
            "_margin": { "unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "18", "left": "0", "isLinked": false }
          },
          "elements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "cp_in_t2",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "text-editor",
          "settings": {
            "editor": "<p>All of our combination programs share the same rate, and our team coordinates every logistical detail, including transfers between venues and fishing plans along the way. All you need to do is relax and enjoy the adventure.</p>",
            "text_color": "#6B7A8D",
            "typography_typography": "custom",
            "typography_font_family": "Bricolage Grotesque",
            "typography_font_size": { "unit": "rem", "size": 1, "sizes": [] },
            "typography_line_height": { "unit": "em", "size": 1.8, "sizes": [] }
          },
          "elements": []
        }
      ]
    },

