          "settings": {
            "editor": "<p>For anglers seeking the most complete Patagonia fishing experience we offer, the Grand Slam combines all three of our operations into one extraordinary journey.</p><p>Over the course of the trip, anglers experience the full range of Patagonia's trout fisheries:</p>",
