          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "text-editor",
          "settings": {
            "editor": "<p>In this program, guests begin their journey at El Atravesado Lodge, continue to Rio Manso Lodge, and finish the adventure at one of our remote River Camps. The itinerary can also be arranged in the reverse order depending on guest preferences and availability.</p><p>From covering big water by drift boat to stalking trout on foot in crystal-clear creeks, the Grand Slam offers an unmatched variety of fisheries and environments.</p><p>This program is designed for anglers who want to fully immerse themselves in Patagonia, exploring its most beautiful waters while enjoying the unique character of each venue.</p>",
